sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他兩集好一般</blockquote><br />\n第一集係講設定<br />\n第二集戲玉<br />\n第三集補完<br />\n完全唔洗dlc</blockquote><br />\n你作嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n事實上係<br />\nNolan話拍第一集嗰時冇諗過會有第二集<br />\n淨係純粹想為batman set up一個origins <br />\n結果第一集叫好叫座先拍第二集<br />\n拍完第二集因為joker嘅超卓表演猶疑咗陣拍唔拍落去<br />\n最後都係決定補完成個系列close file"},{"pid":"15eed821ef178e9bfdf9c6b21bea2b5e6c9fec5b","tid":256513,"uid":18220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Dark Knight Trilogy唔係英雄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解 借左個殼黎用姐</blockquote><br />\n係Nolan屌打<br />\nDark knight只係載體 工具</blockquote><br />\n次次見到tdk唔係英雄片就覺得好笑。<br />\n咩先叫英雄片？</blockquote><br />\n利申左先Marvel DC都有睇<br />\n齋講TDK似鬥智鬥力犯罪片多過英雄片<br />\n感覺上係講Bruce Wayne而唔係Batman"},{"pid":"cb41d5d9ebd83da54c40eeceffe73bc32b6bd8b4","tid":256513,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:15:19.000Z","msg":"DC狗除左Batman，重有乜可以J? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c65a62f719aebd6847209ebe8fa3578a3d249b","tid":256513,"uid":65401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Dark Knight Trilogy唔係英雄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\n勁既係Nolan加入好多人性真實元素落去，<br />\n唔係佢拍應該同其他Superhero相差不遠"},{"pid":"76db97c19e7375b8f9662cc9f9d4bf1fdc03d806","tid":256513,"uid":34970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Dark Knight Trilogy唔係英雄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解 借左個殼黎用姐</blockquote><br />\n係Nolan屌打<br />\nDark knight只係載體 工具</blockquote><br />\n次次見到tdk唔係英雄片就覺得好笑。<br />\n咩先叫英雄片？</blockquote><br />\n利申左先Marvel DC都有睇<br />\n